game.name: Mommy Princess Go Shopping
game.description:
This time we have brought something different, pretty engaging and highly addictive online activity for you ladies! The two lovely Disney princesses named Belle and Rapunzel have recently turned into the lovely mothers. Today they both have planned out to go to their nearby mall and shop for their some needful belongings for themselves and their little babies. Being a new to the city, these princesses do not have any idea how to do it. Join Mommy Princess Go Shopping and help them to sort out this puzzle by shopping for their favorite essentials!
Your objective in this brand new dressing game for girls is to help both the princesses to make a quick decision on every product purchase. Make sure to mix and match as many options as you can and keep experimenting until you find out the one that looks best on them. They also carry their sweet and cute little daughters, so do not forget to buy items for the little babies. Remember they both have limited budget for their shopping. So, help them to select dresses and things that do not affect their budget. 
It will be amazing to play the role of a fashion advisor in this one of the best girls games. These princesses do not want to compromise their looks even after becoming a mommy. Choose the girl you want to shop for with and then select the store from where you want to buy things in this html5 princess dress up game! In Baby Shopping store, you would all the things for their little cute babies, while Happy Mothers store will offer you plenty of options for jeans, tops, gowns, handbags and pair of shoes. Enjoy more girly challenges online on atmegame.com, no download required!
